alternationDuration.name: Duration Before Switching Rotation Visual2 Guides
alternationDuration.description:
The amount of time spent before switching between the dash orb and gravity portal as visual guides for the rotation buttons.

<cy>If changing this setting while inside the editor, you will need to restart the editor for your changes to apply.</c>
